#: doc/src/docbkx/openstack-security/ch025_web-dashboard.xml:97(title)
msgid "Upgrading"
msgstr ""

#: doc/src/docbkx/openstack-security/ch025_web-dashboard.xml:98(para)
msgid ""
"Django security releases are generally well tested and aggressively "
"backwards compatible. In almost all cases, new major releases of Django are "
"also fully backwards compatible with previous releases. Horizon implementers "
"are strongly encouraged to run the latest stable release of Django with up-"
"to-date security releases."
msgstr ""

#: doc/src/docbkx/openstack-security/ch026_compute.xml:10(para)
msgid ""
"OpenStack can be configured to provide remote desktop console access to "
"instances for tenants and/or administrators using the Virtual Network "
"Computer (VNC) protocol.  "
