#: doc/src/docbkx/openstack-security/ch026_compute.xml:4(para)
msgid ""
"The compute service (Nova) is one of the more complex OpenStack services. "
" It runs in many locations throughout the cloud and interacts with a variety "
"of internal services.  For this reason, most of our recommendations "
"regarding best practices for Nova configuration are distributed throughout "
"this book. We provide specific details in the sections on Management, API "
"Endpoints, Messaging, and Database."
